summary: This is a domestic witness travel request form from the SDNY Victim/Witness Unit, dated November 11, 2021, for a fact witness to appear at the trial of Ghislaine Maxwell on December 1, 2021. The witness is identified as a victim-witness and requires hotel accommodations.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: The defendant in the criminal case referenced in the travel request form (United States v. Ghislaine Maxwell).

events.title: Ghislaine Maxwell Trial Witness Appearance
events.description: A fact witness, identified as a victim-witness, is scheduled to appear at the trial of Ghislaine Maxwell in the SDNY.

keyFacts: A victim-witness was scheduled to travel to testify at the Ghislaine Maxwell trial on December 1, 2021.
The travel request was processed by the SDNY Victim/Witness Unit on November 11, 2021.
The witness was to be provided hotel accommodations from December 1 to December 3, 2021.
The witness was a fact witness and not a government employee or facing criminal charges.
The document is a standard administrative form for coordinating witness travel for federal trials.
